title: [BOUNTY] SourceCred Setup
body:
Description: Want to setup SourceCred inside of JAMM Discord to reward engagement with existing community members. Community members will be rewarded with JAMM based on the amount of JS emojis they receive relative to other members.

Website: https://sourcecred.io/

Bounty: 5K $JAMM
author: 0x565B93a15d38aCD79c120b15432D21E21eD274d6
